org.cyclonedx.maven

Interface ModelConverter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultModelConverter

    public interface ModelConverter
    Model converter from Maven concepts (dependency Artifact + MavenProject) to CycloneDX ones (resp. Component with pURL + Metadata).
